1
00:00:18,280 --> 00:00:19,120
Boss Bai.

2
00:00:40,039 --> 00:00:40,880
We finally meet.

3
00:00:41,240 --> 00:00:43,000
And I finally see what a scumbag

4
00:00:43,000 --> 00:00:43,880
you really look like.

5
00:00:44,039 --> 00:00:44,679
You...

6
00:00:50,799 --> 00:00:51,840
Did you bring the stuff?

7
00:00:52,159 --> 00:00:53,840
You turned my daughter against me,

8
00:00:53,840 --> 00:00:55,759
and made Qiqi steal the title deed for the inheritance.

9
00:00:55,759 --> 00:00:57,039
Money this dirty,

10
00:00:57,399 --> 00:00:58,799
can you really spend it with a clear conscience?

11
00:00:59,000 --> 00:01:01,119
If there were no bad blood between you,

12
00:01:01,119 --> 00:01:02,759
no outsider could've driven you apart.

13
00:01:02,759 --> 00:01:03,880
Enough of your nonsense.

14
00:01:04,159 --> 00:01:04,840
Hurry up.

15
00:01:04,840 --> 00:01:06,280
Show me what's in the inheritance.

16
00:01:06,879 --> 00:01:08,159
You want the title deed,

17
00:01:08,159 --> 00:01:09,239
the jewelry,

18
00:01:09,480 --> 00:01:11,439
the deposits, or the trust fund?

19
00:01:12,239 --> 00:01:14,439
Who stops at just one bite of meat?

20
00:01:14,439 --> 00:01:15,840
Of course, I want it all.

21
00:01:15,840 --> 00:01:17,319
Quite an appetite you've got.

22
00:01:17,480 --> 00:01:18,040
Too bad.

23
00:01:18,319 --> 00:01:19,719
I'm afraid you can't swallow it all.

24
00:01:20,519 --> 00:01:21,560
Don't you worry.

25
00:01:21,879 --> 00:01:23,799
When I eat,

26
00:01:24,159 --> 00:01:25,680
I lick the plate clean.

27
00:01:50,799 --> 00:01:52,879
Fifteen million.

28
00:01:57,760 --> 00:01:59,519
There's actually fifteen million here.

29
00:01:59,519 --> 00:02:00,879
How do I withdraw this money?

30
00:02:01,480 --> 00:02:02,560
What if I told you

31
00:02:02,560 --> 00:02:04,439
this is how Wang Kechen conned girls,

32
00:02:04,439 --> 00:02:05,840
would you believe me?

33
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:06,840
I don't believe you.

34
00:02:06,840 --> 00:02:08,439
If you don't believe me, look it up online.

35
00:02:08,879 --> 00:02:10,039
This trust fund

36
00:02:10,039 --> 00:02:11,360
doesn't even exist.

37
00:02:11,360 --> 00:02:12,560
It's all a lie.

38
00:02:13,080 --> 00:02:14,360
I never dared tell my daughter,

39
00:02:14,560 --> 00:02:16,080
afraid she couldn't take the blow.

40
00:02:16,680 --> 00:02:17,639
A father

41
00:02:17,840 --> 00:02:18,919
using a fake inheritance

42
00:02:19,280 --> 00:02:20,680
to trick his daughter into loving him.

43
00:02:20,680 --> 00:02:22,000
He's really something.

44
00:02:22,360 --> 00:02:23,520
If nothing had gone wrong,

45
00:02:23,520 --> 00:02:25,919
he would've lured Qiqi away from me.

46
00:02:27,479 --> 00:02:28,639
Who are you trying to fool?

47
00:02:30,319 --> 00:02:31,039
Looks like

48
00:02:31,520 --> 00:02:33,400
I need to turn up the heat on you.

49
00:02:34,039 --> 00:02:35,719
Should I post her private photos

50
00:02:35,719 --> 00:02:37,680
all over the internet?

51
00:02:38,039 --> 00:02:38,800
Or

52
00:02:39,080 --> 00:02:41,479
just chop off a few of her fingers

53
00:02:41,479 --> 00:02:42,639
to save your life?

54
00:02:43,719 --> 00:02:44,520
Qiqi.

55
00:02:44,759 --> 00:02:46,560
Mom didn't take good care of you before.

56
00:02:47,080 --> 00:02:48,599
Now Mom will get rid of

57
00:02:48,599 --> 00:02:50,360
the biggest trouble in your life.

58
00:02:51,479 --> 00:02:52,879
Chu Feng, we've got trouble!

59
00:02:52,879 --> 00:02:53,919
Boss Bai's on the run!

60
00:02:54,479 --> 00:02:54,879
What happened?

61
00:02:54,879 --> 00:02:56,479
Take it easy, slow down.

62
00:02:57,199 --> 00:02:58,520
She asked how to get back at that scumbag,

63
00:02:58,840 --> 00:02:59,879
then took a cab and took off.

64
00:03:00,159 --> 00:03:01,840
I checked with the taxi company.

65
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:04,080
She went to the abandoned building out east,

66
00:03:04,360 --> 00:03:05,800
diagonally across from the soda factory.

67
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:06,439
Got it.

68
00:03:06,919 --> 00:03:07,840
Wait for us there.

69
00:03:07,840 --> 00:03:09,080
Qin Mo and I are nearby.

70
00:03:09,240 --> 00:03:09,840
I'll head over and check.

71
00:03:37,520 --> 00:03:38,039
Captain Chu.

72
00:03:38,639 --> 00:03:40,120
There's something here, a photo album.

73
00:03:40,400 --> 00:03:40,960
Chu Feng.

74
00:03:41,759 --> 00:03:42,400
Did you find her?

75
00:03:43,479 --> 00:03:44,240
What are you doing here?

76
00:03:44,680 --> 00:03:45,479
It's dangerous!

77
00:03:47,159 --> 00:03:47,800
Be careful.

78
00:03:48,319 --> 00:03:48,719
It's okay.

79
00:03:56,599 --> 00:03:58,520
This is my mom and Wang Kechen.

80
00:03:58,719 --> 00:03:59,840
That little girl is you.

81
00:04:00,759 --> 00:04:02,439
Then Boss Bai must be nearby.

82
00:04:02,439 --> 00:04:03,879
I've never seen this album before.

83
00:04:04,520 --> 00:04:05,000
Mom!

84
00:04:05,439 --> 00:04:06,120
Mom! Boss Bai!

85
00:04:18,360 --> 00:04:19,079
Mom!

86
00:04:19,519 --> 00:04:20,240
Mom!

87
00:04:25,519 --> 00:04:26,560
Mom!

88
00:04:33,839 --> 00:04:35,000
Qin Mo, come with me!

89
00:04:35,000 --> 00:04:36,360
Tianfang, get her out of here!

90
00:04:36,600 --> 00:04:37,160
Take her away!

91
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:21,560
This rope's been tampered with.

92
00:05:21,800 --> 00:05:22,720
The moment you touch it,

93
00:05:22,720 --> 00:05:23,680
the body will drop.

94
00:05:34,120 --> 00:05:35,560
You want to die, huh?

95
00:05:35,560 --> 00:05:36,800
I'll grant your wish.

96
00:05:48,879 --> 00:05:49,360
Brother Hui!

97
00:05:52,120 --> 00:05:53,360
Want to take me down with you?

98
00:05:54,279 --> 00:05:54,639
Brother Hui!

99
00:05:54,959 --> 00:05:55,720
Watch this.

100
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:21,000
Captain Chu.

101
00:06:22,160 --> 00:06:23,360
This character has an extra stroke.

102
00:06:23,680 --> 00:06:24,519
Looks intentional.

103
00:06:29,040 --> 00:06:30,720
This is clearly Ma Xiaojun's doing.

104
00:06:31,120 --> 00:06:32,519
He barely had any schooling.

105
00:06:35,519 --> 00:06:36,319
Notify the Evidence Department.

106
00:06:41,160 --> 00:06:41,600
Hello.

107
00:06:41,879 --> 00:06:42,480
Evidence Department.

108
00:06:43,439 --> 00:06:44,720
We need evidence collection on-site.

109
00:07:06,560 --> 00:07:08,800
Chen Hui and Ma Xiaojun committed serial crimes.

110
00:07:09,240 --> 00:07:10,639
The nature of their crimes is extremely severe.

111
00:07:11,040 --> 00:07:11,959
Our superiors have ordered us

112
00:07:12,240 --> 00:07:13,959
to immediately form a special task force.

113
00:07:14,279 --> 00:07:15,279
We must, as soon as possible,

114
00:07:15,439 --> 00:07:16,759
bring both men to justice.

115
00:07:16,959 --> 00:07:17,600
Everyone,

116
00:07:17,720 --> 00:07:18,560
give it everything you've got.

117
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:20,079
Chu Feng.

118
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:21,480
Here.

119
00:07:21,720 --> 00:07:23,399
You'll lead the task force.

120
00:07:23,759 --> 00:07:24,199
Yes, sir.

121
00:07:25,480 --> 00:07:26,319
From this moment on,

122
00:07:26,720 --> 00:07:28,959
Tech, CID, all units must coordinate.

123
00:07:28,959 --> 00:07:29,759
Share all leads.

124
00:07:29,759 --> 00:07:30,680
Hold each person accountable.

125
00:07:31,360 --> 00:07:32,800
We must root out Chen Dahui.

126
00:07:33,920 --> 00:07:34,600
Qin Mo.

127
00:07:35,720 --> 00:07:36,160
Here.

128
00:07:37,560 --> 00:07:38,519
Due to the recusal rule,

129
00:07:38,720 --> 00:07:40,000
you must step away from this investigation.

130
00:07:42,279 --> 00:07:42,800
Yes, sir.

131
00:07:45,160 --> 00:07:45,680
Sun Bo.

132
00:07:46,120 --> 00:07:46,759
You'll take her place.

133
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:47,560
Yes, sir.

134
00:07:52,920 --> 00:07:53,360
Good.

135
00:07:53,720 --> 00:07:54,480
The entire bureau

136
00:07:54,480 --> 00:07:56,800
will fully support the task force.

137
00:07:56,959 --> 00:07:58,000
Whatever support you need,

138
00:07:58,480 --> 00:07:59,560
just ask directly.

139
00:07:59,759 --> 00:08:00,240
Chu Feng.

140
00:08:01,040 --> 00:08:02,519
I have only one demand.

141
00:08:02,720 --> 00:08:04,279
You must crack this case immediately.

142
00:08:04,279 --> 00:08:05,519
Restore peace to our society.

143
00:08:05,959 --> 00:08:06,480
Understood.

144
00:08:07,759 --> 00:08:09,839
The arrest team began a citywide search.

145
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:11,160
We urgently need to establish

146
00:08:11,160 --> 00:08:12,600
a surveillance analysis team.

147
00:08:12,879 --> 00:08:13,399
Sun Bo.

148
00:08:13,399 --> 00:08:13,879
Yes, sir.

149
00:08:13,879 --> 00:08:14,720
You're in charge.

150
00:08:14,879 --> 00:08:15,920
Through video analysis,

151
00:08:16,199 --> 00:08:17,519
quickly identify the escape routes

152
00:08:17,519 --> 00:08:19,199
of Chen Dahui and Ma Xiaojun.

153
00:08:19,560 --> 00:08:20,120
Understood.

154
00:08:22,240 --> 00:08:23,000
Move out, everyone.

155
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:24,000
Yes, sir. Yes, sir.

156
00:08:34,080 --> 00:08:34,799
Qiqi.

157
00:08:35,679 --> 00:08:36,799
Say something.

158
00:08:37,720 --> 00:08:38,720
If... if you're

159
00:08:39,080 --> 00:08:39,600
hurting,

160
00:08:39,919 --> 00:08:41,159
it's okay to cry.

161
00:08:41,600 --> 00:08:42,799
Don't hold it in.

162
00:08:43,279 --> 00:08:44,480
Losing a loved one

163
00:08:44,480 --> 00:08:45,360
can easily trigger

164
00:08:45,360 --> 00:08:47,879
an acute transient psychotic disorder.

165
00:08:48,600 --> 00:08:50,399
Due to an extreme stress response,

166
00:08:50,399 --> 00:08:52,480
patients may experience mood swings.

167
00:08:52,480 --> 00:08:53,240
However,

168
00:08:53,240 --> 00:08:54,759
it can be cured with timely medication.

169
00:08:55,399 --> 00:08:56,000
Okay.

170
00:08:57,120 --> 00:08:58,639
He Siqi, time for your medicine.

171
00:09:00,679 --> 00:09:01,679
Come on, take your medicine.

172
00:09:04,759 --> 00:09:05,399
Careful, it's hot.

173
00:09:06,399 --> 00:09:07,519
Did my mom come see me?

174
00:09:07,720 --> 00:09:08,799
Did she come to visit me?

175
00:09:09,960 --> 00:09:10,919
Say something!

176
00:09:11,080 --> 00:09:11,879
Just leave it, I'll handle it.

177
00:09:13,000 --> 00:09:13,960
She's coming, she's coming.

178
00:09:14,480 --> 00:09:15,759
Let's take the medicine first,

179
00:09:15,759 --> 00:09:17,240
and then Mom will come back.

180
00:09:18,639 --> 00:09:19,480
I won't take it.

181
00:09:20,600 --> 00:09:21,639
If my mom doesn't come,

182
00:09:21,639 --> 00:09:22,480
I won't take it.

183
00:09:22,639 --> 00:09:23,320
She's having

184
00:09:23,559 --> 00:09:24,559
hallucinations and delusions.

185
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:26,480
Deep down, she probably can't

186
00:09:26,480 --> 00:09:27,759
accept her mother's death.

187
00:09:27,919 --> 00:09:28,600
Please try to talk her into it.

188
00:09:34,720 --> 00:09:35,320
Qiqi.

189
00:09:35,600 --> 00:09:36,600
You're sick right now.

190
00:09:37,240 --> 00:09:38,519
Only if you take your medicine

191
00:09:39,120 --> 00:09:40,240
will Mom come back.

192
00:09:42,159 --> 00:09:42,679
Be a good girl.

193
00:09:44,440 --> 00:09:45,080
Take it.

194
00:09:45,799 --> 00:09:46,679
You're lying to me.

195
00:09:46,679 --> 00:09:47,960
My mom isn't coming.

196
00:09:47,960 --> 00:09:48,960
She doesn't want me anymore.

197
00:09:48,960 --> 00:09:50,080
She's abandoned me.

198
00:09:50,360 --> 00:09:51,320
No, no.

199
00:09:51,840 --> 00:09:53,799
Mom loves you most in this world.

200
00:09:53,799 --> 00:09:55,240
How could she ever abandon you?

201
00:09:56,320 --> 00:09:57,120
Be good now.

202
00:09:57,840 --> 00:09:59,399
If you love Mom too,

203
00:10:00,080 --> 00:10:01,200
you can't make her worry.

204
00:10:01,480 --> 00:10:02,200
Right?

205
00:10:03,200 --> 00:10:04,200
It's all my fault.

206
00:10:05,159 --> 00:10:06,320
It's all my fault.

207
00:10:06,559 --> 00:10:07,200
Be good now.

208
00:10:07,200 --> 00:10:08,080
She doesn't want me anymore.

209
00:10:09,279 --> 00:10:10,240
It's okay, it's okay.

210
00:10:10,639 --> 00:10:11,240
She's abandoned me.
